        <Parent_String>animal material by egg and egg components [300191706], animal material by form or function [300191588], animal material [300011793], biological material [300265629], materials by origin [300206573], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
